  "text": "What would the difference be? I am Ra. If one wishes to have power over an entity it is an aid to know that entity's name. If one wishes no power over an entity but wishes to collect that entity into the very heart of one's own being it is well to forget the naming. Both processes are magically viable. Each is polarized in a specific way. It is your choice.",
